    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>European armors used in war by heavy cavalry up to the end of the 16th century, consisting of an armor with matching bard.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
